name: O & Bzjm skate somewhere in Kota Bandung
description:
Awkward Adventure skate series 09/50 presents: O & Bzjm skate somewhere in Kota Bandung.

This spot is legendary. Some say that a molotov threw and exploded while bunch of skaters had a session of fun there.

Drawing pen on paper with digitalized coloring to achieve 80's comic style.

December 2021.
